name: 亚历克斯·阿瑟罗 Alex Arsenault
intro: Born on. February 28, 1985. IMDb. Alex Arsenault portrays Philo, a Graystone Industries robotics technician who helped design the U-87 robot. Arsenault is an actor, known for Caprica (SyFy), "Supernatural" (CW) and "Fairly Legal" (USA Network).
birthplace: 加拿大,萨斯喀彻温省,里贾纳
